<span class="textbox">Truman starts yelling, asking what's going on and what they are doing to her. A paremedic turns to Truman and says, "I'm so sorry, sir. This patient escaped the Seaside Psychiatric Ward earlier this morning. She's been having severe delusions. She thinks everyone's an actor. Don't worry. She's getting the help she needs now."</span>

<span class="bottom-left">[[Continue|Truman Goes Back Home][$suspicion += 3, $ratings += 2]]</span>


