<span class="textbox">Truman is able to get into his car. He starts the car, turns on the radio, and starts to drive to work. While he is on the way to work, he starts to hear strange things on the radio. It seems like the radio is connecting to the crew's broadcast.</span>

<span class="bottom-left">[[Fix the radio and have the radio broadcaster claim it was atmospheric interference ->Newspaper stand][$suspicion += 1]]</span>

<span class="bottom-right">[[Have two cars crash into eachother infront of him ->Newspaper stand][$ratings += 1, $funding -= 1]]</span>


